locality: Road S from Yate to Goro Village (Xere), near Kuebini River

Bois du Sud. End of side road SE from Noumea-Yate road, near stream (currently dry) and picnic area. Side of track at ecotone between a small patch of forest near stream and maquis minier, on ultramafic substrate.
Plateau du Tango. Pine plantation with patches of native vegetation, especially in gullies.
By roadside towards bottom of Duzmac road.
